reviewText: I bought this for a big Tina fan friend of mine. I didn't watch it and I know nothing about it. But, he was thrilled.

SEE TINA IN FULL ACTION BEFORE HER PRIVATE DANCER COMEBACK.
SONGS INCLUDE.
-NUTBUSH CITY LIMITS
-RIVER DEEP
-HOT LEGS
-ACID QUEEN
-FEVER
-PROUD MARY
-BITCH IS BACK
-I CAN'T TURN YOU LOOSE
-MUSIC KEEPS ME DANCING
-HONKY TONK WOMAN
-I WANT TO TAKE YOU HIGHER
-DISCO FEVER
YOU DON'T SEE PERFORMERS LIKE TINA ANYMORE.
